---
title: Login Flow
config:
  theme: neutral
  look: classic
  layout: dagre
---
sequenceDiagram
  participant user as user-client
  participant api as auth-api
  participant db as user-db

  user->>api: submits credentials
  api->>db: fetches user record
  db-->>api: returns user data
  alt credentials valid
    api-->>user: returns access token
  else credentials invalid
    api--xuser: returns auth error
  end
